{"tid":2122583,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"新華社：關閉美國總領館  只針對華府少數極端勢力","createTime":"2020-07-24T05:28:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-24T05:31:32.000Z","uid":7542,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"877e577eb9224e9ea0ea492c3caae01933bb6d41","tid":2122583,"uid":7542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T05:28:22.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">分化</span>華府員工</strong></span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n中國外交部通知美方，關閉美國駐成都總領事館。新華社發表社評，認為美方霸凌挑釁在先，中方被逼無奈反制在後，責任完全在美方。 社評說，美方蠻橫要求中方閉館之舉，嚴重違反中美領事條約有關規定，是美方對中方單方面發起的又一次政治挑釁，認為美方聲稱關閉中國駐休斯敦總領館的理由，是完全站不住腳。　　<br />\n<br />\n社評又指，中國一貫高度重視中美關係，今次被迫採取反制措施，是對美方無理行徑的正當和必要反應，符合國際法及外交慣例，強調此舉只針對美國政府少數極端勢力，不針對美國人民。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1539633-20200724.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1539633-20200724.htm&d=7JJHJI7m8dwGfBTVwC1i6MbSs98ObMNNw7VTZDCdQw4%3D&h=2edf4d3e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1539633-20200724.htm&h=f3cf7956\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1539633-20200724.htm</a>"},{"pid":"c8219a0679e6990dc3c6ebe2bc779695f0f72058","tid":2122583,"uid":183758,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T05:29:29.000Z","msg":"好撚低裝呀d老土分化橋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ceede8a6de62e83e20d17cbe8ec35c69f693c7d2","tid":2122583,"uid":183758,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"877e577eb9224e9ea0ea492c3caae01933bb6d41","tid":2122583,"uid":7542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T05:28:22.000Z","msg":"<span class=\